query.pigql: a= load "${App.EdgeMarts.opportunity_products.Alias}";a = filter a by 'Opportunity.Owner.Role.ParentRoleId' in {{ results(Id_1, 'UserRoleId') }} ; a = group a by 'Opportunity.Owner.Name';a = foreach a generate 'Opportunity.Owner.Name' as 'Opportunity.Owner.Name',  first('Opportunity.Owner.Name') as 'Direct Reports';
